headline: SWEP Introduces New Products for Future Demands of Data Center Cooling and Heat Reuse
summary: SWEP, part of Dover (NYSE: DOV) and a world-leading supplier of brazed plate heat exchangers (BPHEs), today announced the launch of two new products, SWEP B327 and SWEP B224, developed to meet growing market demand in data center cooling and district energy applications.

headline: Dover (DOV): Evaluating Whether This Quiet Industrial Compounder Still Trades Below Its Fair Value
summary: Dover (DOV) has been quietly rewarding patient shareholders, with the stock up around 3% over the past month and roughly 7% in the past 3 months, outpacing many industrial peers.
